NAME
       ballerina-tool-update - Update to the latest patch version within the
       minor version of the currently active tool version

SYNOPSIS
       bal tool update <tool-id>

OPTIONS
       -h, --help
           Print the usage details of tool the update command.

DESCRIPTION
       Fetch the latest compatible version that is within the currently active
       version's minor version of a given tool from Ballerina Central
       repository and set it as the active version.
